---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Documentation — gpulse"
  description="Complete documentation for gpulse GPU monitoring tool. Learn about views, leak detection, themes, keyboard shortcuts, and configuration."
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Documentation</h1>
  <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed">
    Everything you need to know about gpulse — from first install to advanced leak detection.
  </p>

  <!-- Getting Started -->
  <div class="mt-12">
    <a
      href="/docs/getting-started"
      class="group block rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_-5px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)]"
    >
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-cyan/10">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-cyan" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.59 14.37a6 6 0 01-5.84 7.38v-4.8m5.84-2.58a14.98 14.98 0 006.16-12.12A14.98 14.98 0 009.631 8.41m5.96 5.96a14.926 14.926 0 01-5.841 2.58m-.119-8.54a6 6 0 00-7.381 5.84h4.8m2.581-5.84a14.927 14.927 0 00-2.58 5.841m2.699-5.959a6.001 6.001 0 00-.599-.299" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Getting Started</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Install gpulse, launch the dashboard, and understand the basics in under five minutes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Views Section -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-bold">Views</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Seven purpose-built monitoring modes, each a single keystroke away.</p>

  <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="/docs/views/grid"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Grid View</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Default multi-GPU tile layout with all key metrics at a glance.</p>
      <span class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted/60">
        <kbd class="rounded border border-border bg-dark px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-cyan">v</kbd>
        default view
      </span>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/views/detail"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Detail View</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Deep dive into a single GPU with full process table and metrics.</p>
      <span class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted/60">
        <kbd class="rounded border border-border bg-dark px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-cyan">d</kbd>
        to activate
      </span>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/views/list"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">List View</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Compact table view for dense information at a glance.</p>
      <span class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted/60">
        <kbd class="rounded border border-border bg-dark px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-cyan">v</kbd>
        cycle views
      </span>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/views/predict"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Predict View</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">OOM prediction with leak detection algorithms and time-to-OOM estimates.</p>
      <span class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted/60">
        <kbd class="rounded border border-border bg-dark px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-cyan">P</kbd>
        to activate
      </span>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/views/compare"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Compare View</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Side-by-side GPU comparison for spotting imbalances.</p>
      <span class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted/60">
        <kbd class="rounded border border-border bg-dark px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-cyan">c</kbd>
        to activate
      </span>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/views/topology"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Topology View</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">GPU interconnect diagram showing bus topology and links.</p>
      <span class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted/60">
        <kbd class="rounded border border-border bg-dark px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-cyan">g</kbd>
        to activate
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-bold">Features</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Core capabilities that make gpulse more than a simple monitor.</p>

  <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="/docs/leak-detection"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Leak Detection</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Three detection algorithms analyze memory growth patterns in real time, predicting OOM before it happens.</p>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/themes"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Themes</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">15 built-in color themes including accessibility-optimized colorblind-safe options.</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Guides Section -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-bold">Guides</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">How-to guides for common workflows and advanced configuration.</p>

  <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="/docs/multi-gpu"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Multi-GPU Monitoring</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Grid view, sorting, detail deep-dive, compare, topology, and 16+ GPU pagination.</p>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/metrics"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Understanding Metrics</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">What each GPU metric measures, normal ranges, and when to be concerned.</p>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/customization"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Customization</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">15 themes, recommended fonts, terminal emulator settings, and keybinding reference.</p>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/performance"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Performance Tuning</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Optimize monitoring intervals, history size, database settings, and leak detection sensitivity.</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference Section -->
  <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-bold">Reference</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Quick-access tables and configuration details.</p>

  <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="/docs/keyboard"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Complete keybinding reference for every view and action.</p>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/configuration"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">Configuration</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Config file location, TOML options, and environment variable overrides.</p>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/faq"
      class="group rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 transition-all duration-200 hover:border-cyan/30"
    >
      <h3 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors">FAQ</h3>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">Answers to frequently asked questions about gpulse.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
